strings.Value: "Ye-e-eah, ha, ha, ha, hmm... I've never spent a night in such a hellhole — even when Octavia and I were on the run from the Technic League..."
"An atmospheric place. I wouldn't recommend it to my friends though. Ha!"
"Pff. What, want a feather-bed? You should see the places I sleeped in..."
"I don't think I would choose to camp here... But {name} decided we should. No doubt, {mf|he|she} had {mf|his|her} reasons."
"I have no quarrel with dirt and damp. But keep your weapons close tonight."
"In times like this, I imagine that I am far, far away. Or that my friends are with me — and what could be better than that?"
"You should have seen where our camp was. So cozy! Smells there strong. Lots of us always sleep because of fumes!"
